<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Congratulations on Becoming a Seller</title>
    <style>
      /* Fonts */ @import
      url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,700&display=swap");
      /* Global styles */ body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: "Roboto",
      sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; } /* Container styles */ .container
      { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px; background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e6e6e6; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,
      0, 0, 0.1); } /* Heading styles */ h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight:
      bold; color: #333; text-align: center; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 30px;
      } /* Paragraph styles */ p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color:
      #666; margin: 20px 0; text-align: justify; } /* Verification code styles
      */ .code { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #0066ff; text-align:
      center; margin: 30px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
      border-radius: 5px; background-color: #f5f5f5; } /* Button styles */ .btn
      { display: block; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 40px; padding: 15px 25px;
      max-width: 200px; width: 100%; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff;
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; border-radius:
      5px; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: center; transition: all
      0.2s ease-in-out; } /* Button hover styles */ .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0062cc; transform: scale(1.05); } /* Media queries */
      @media screen and (max-width: 640px) { .container { padding: 20px; } h1 {
      font-size: 24px; } p { font-size: 16px; } .code { font-size: 24px;
      padding: 15px; } .btn { font-size: 18px; padding: 12px 20px; max-width:
      160px; color: #fff; } }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Congratulations {{username}}, You're Now a Seller!</h1>
    <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
    <p>
      Thank you for applying to become a seller on our platform. We're pleased
      to inform you that your application has been approved and you are now a
      registered seller.
    </p>
    <p>
      In order to start selling, you need to verify your account. Please use the
      following verification code to verify your account:
    </p>
    <p class="code" id="verification-code">{{verificationCode}}</p>
    <p>
      The verification code will expire in 24 hours. Please verify your account
      before then.
    </p>
    <p>
      To login as a seller, please follow these steps:
      <ol>
        <li>Go to our main website at {{verificationLink}}</li>
        <li>Enter your login credentials (username and password) and click "Sign
          In"</li>
        <li>Check your email for a message from us with the subject line
          "QuickCart Seller Verification Code"</li>
        <li>Open the email and copy the verification code provided</li>
        <li>Return to the QuickCart website and enter the verification code
          when prompted</li>
        <li>You will be asked to create a new password. Please enter a strong
          and unique password that you will remember.</li>
        <li>Once you have verified your account and created a password, you will
          be logged in as a seller and can start creating listings.</li>
      </ol>
    </p>
    <p>
      If you did not request this verification code, please ignore this email.
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for choosing our platform to sell your products. We look forward
      to seeing your listings!
    </p>
  </body>
</html>